<div class="title">Am I in a Dream? Whoa, I Am in a Dream</div>
<div class="substance">Kava & Alcohol</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=The+Jake&Exact=1">The Jake</a></div>


